PN,32201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FCumbria's Luke Greenbank has been
OL,8,Fselected to be the baton bearer for
OL,9,FEngland for the Glasgow 2026
OL,10,FCommonwealth Games Opening Ceremony on
OL,11,FThursday 23 July.
OL,13,FThe Commonwealth Games return to
OL,14,FGlasgow in 2026, from July 23rd until
OL,15,FAugust 2nd and it will be Luke
OL,16,FGreenbank's third Commonwealth Games,
OL,17,Fhaving won silver in the men's 4x100m
OL,18,Fmedley relay at Gold Coast 2018 before
OL,19,Fupgrading to gold at Birmingham 2022.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FHe told ITV Border "for me as a baton
OL,8,Fbearer, it's nice to represent them
OL,9,F(his fellow athletes) and be the face
OL,10,Fof Team England".
OL,12,FGames organisers said, "England's
OL,13,Fbaton was decorated by Cornish artist
OL,14,FBonnie Steward using plastics
OL,15,Fcollected from beaches and urban
OL,16,Fspaces, transformed into vibrant
OL,17,Fmosaics celebrating England's
OL,18,Fidentity."
OL,26,@qD@ApmqD@Upn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FThe backstroke specialist from
OL,8,FCockermouth is also an Olympic and
OL,9,Fmultiple World Championship medallist.
OL,10,FHe became the first British man to win
OL,11,Fan Olympic medal in the 200m
OL,12,Fbackstroke when he claimed bronze at
OL,13,FTokyo 2020, where he also won silver
OL,14,Fas part of Great Britain's medley
OL,15,Frelay team.
OL,17,FOrganisers say beyond his achievements
OL,18,Fin the pool, Greenbank was nominated
OL,19,F"in recognition of his
OL,20,Fprofessionalism, humility and team-
OL,21,Ffirst approach".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FThey continued, "Calm and composed in
OL,8,Fthe highest-pressure environments, he
OL,9,Fis respected across the team as an
OL,10,Fathlete whose standards and quiet
OL,11,Fleadership elevate those around him."
OL,13,FLuke Greenbank said, "I knew I had
OL,14,Fbeen nominated by Swim England, but I
OL,15,Fwasn't really expecting anything."
OL,26,@uD@VOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FHe continued, "It's not something
OL,8,Fswimmers usually get to experience
OL,9,Fbecause we're competing from day one,
OL,10,Fbut because my events are a little
OL,11,Flater in the programme, I'll be able
OL,12,Fto attend. It'll be a great experience
OL,13,Fand I'm really proud to represent the
OL,14,Fteam."
OL,16,FGlasgow is the third city in history
OL,17,Fto host the games twice. Glasgow is
OL,18,Fslightly closer to home for Luke
OL,19,FGreenbank than Birmingham was.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FThe Team England Swimmer says he is
OL,8,Fexcited to compete and feels like he
OL,9,Fis in good shape but he is aware of
OL,10,Fthe challenge and says he's looking
OL,11,Fforward to putting what he's been
OL,12,Fworking on into practice and hopefully
OL,13,F"bringing home a few medals for
OL,14,FEngland".
OL,16,FLawn bowler Sian Honnor has been
OL,17,Fselected to be Team England's flag
OL,18,Fbearer.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FThe pair were chosen following a vote
OL,8,Fby their fellow Team England athletes,
OL,9,Fhaving been nominated by their sports
OL,10,Fin recognition of their achievements,
OL,11,Fleadership and the example they set to
OL,12,Fthose around them.
OL,14,FGlasgow 2026 will be Sian Honnor's
OL,15,Ffifth Commonwealth Games appearance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FThe Canterbury bowler has won a medal
OL,8,Fat each of the past four Games,
OL,9,Fcollecting women's triples gold at
OL,10,FGlasgow 2014 and Birmingham 2022,
OL,11,Falongside bronze medals at Gold Coast
OL,12,F2018 and Delhi 2010. She will compete
OL,13,Fin the women's pairs alongside Amy
OL,14,FPharaoh in Glasgow.
OL,16,FShe told ITV Border, "To be voted in
OL,17,Fby my fellow athletes, can't describe
OL,18,Fthe feeling and so excited."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FSian and Luke will bear that honour,
OL,8,Fstarting the games tomorrow. Honnor
OL,9,Fwill carry the St George's Cross,
OL,10,Fwhile Greenbank will carry the baton
OL,11,Fas Team England makes its entrance at
OL,12,Fthe Opening Ceremony.
OL,14,FFor the first time, all 74
OL,15,FCommonwealth nations and territories
OL,16,Fhave received their own baton to
OL,17,Fdecorate in celebration of their
OL,18,Fculture, before they reunite at the
OL,19,FOpening Ceremony.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FSian Honnor said: "I've been so lucky
OL,8,Fto travel all around the world to do
OL,9,Fthe sport that I love and compete in
OL,10,Flots of different places.
OL,12,F"But I think there is no greater
OL,13,Ffeeling than having that England shirt
OL,14,Fon your back. It is such a proud
OL,15,Fmoment every time I go out there
OL,16,Frepresenting my country."
OL,26,@oD@SOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784751302
OL,3,CCumbrian swimmer Luke Greenbank is
OL,4,CEngland's Commonwealth Games baton
OL,5,Cbearer
OL,7,FTeam England Chef de Mission Jonny
OL,8,FRiall said: "I am absolutely delighted
OL,9,Fthat Sian and Luke will lead Team
OL,10,FEngland into the Opening Ceremony as
OL,11,Four flag and baton bearers.
OL,13,F"From the outset, we wanted to
OL,14,Frecognise athletes who not only
OL,15,Frepresent their sport with
OL,16,Fdistinction, but who also embody
OL,17,Feverything it means to represent Team
OL,18,FEngland. They are respected by
OL,19,Fteammates, admired by competitors and,
OL,20,Fabove all, wear the England shirt with
OL,21,Fimmense pride."
OL,26,@pD@MOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
